title: Dear Owen Wilson: GRETA TITELMAN LOVES GUY FIERI
itunes:title: Dear Owen Wilson: GRETA TITELMAN LOVES GUY FIERI
description:
Blair Socci, host of the podcast Dear Owen Wilson, welcomes her dear friend, Greta Titelman (Los Espookys, Search Party) to the show. She comes on to profess her love to a certain rockin' chef.

Blair's Show In LA - Monday, JUNE 6th, at The Elysian Theater (featuring Greta Titelman and Carmen Christopher)
